# Notes API â€“ Backend Service

RESTful Notes API built with **Node.js**, **Express**, **MongoDB**, **Redis**, and **Docker**.

This backend service demonstrates clean architecture, standardized API responses, caching with Redis, API documentation using Swagger, and containerized deployment.

---

## âœ¨ Features

- CRUD Notes (Create, Read, Update, Delete)
- RESTful API with Express
- MongoDB as primary database
- Redis caching for read optimization
- JWT Authentication
- Swagger (OpenAPI) documentation
- Postman collection for API testing
- Docker & Docker Compose setup

