---

## ğŸ”„ API Flow

1. Client sends HTTP request
2. Router matches endpoint
3. JWT middleware validates token
4. Controller handles business logic
5. Redis is checked for cached data
6. MongoDB is queried if cache miss
7. API returns standardized response

---

