## ğŸ“¦ API Response Format

### Success
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {}
}

Error
{
  "status": "fail",
  "message": "Error message"
}

ğŸ§  Redis Caching Strategy

Cache is used for read-heavy endpoints

Redis is checked before MongoDB

MongoDB remains the source of truth

Cache is invalidated on write operations

ğŸ³ Docker Setup

Run backend with all dependencies:

docker-compose up --build


Services included:

API

MongoDB

Redis

âš™ï¸ Environment Variables

Create a .env file:

